# 2026-06-03 sweep: keep the build context out of the bytes graveyard.
# - C:    Stray dir created by a Windows uv invocation that stripped the
#         drive colon — produced a literal `C:` subtree containing
#         `C:/Users/.../uv-cache/...` paths. Buildkit chokes on the
#         path shape ("invalid file request") so we exclude it
#         defensively in case it returns.
# - models/         Downloaded HF / SBERT model weights (e.g.
#                   bge-small-domain-ft, ~1.8 GB). Models live in HF_HOME
#                   at runtime, never baked in.
# - bench_results/  Local benchmark output (per-run JSON). Build artefact.
# - retrieval_threshold_sweep.csv  Local eval scratch file.
# - run_eval*.py    One-shot eval drivers; not imported by the app.
C:
models/
bench_results/
retrieval_threshold_sweep.csv
run_eval*.py
